entry.title: The Multilateral Investment Guarantee Agency (Overseas Territories) Order 1988
entry.summary: This Order extends the provisions of sections 3, 4, 5 and 6 of the Multilateral Investment Guarantee Agency Act, subject to modifications and exceptions, to the Territories specified in Schedule 2 hereto.

entry.title: The Merchant Shipping Act 1979 (Cayman Islands) Order 1988
The Wages (Northern Ireland) Order 1988
entry.summary: In this Order part II makes fresh provision for the protection of workers in relation to the payment of wages and part III revises the scope of operation and powers of wages councils.

entry.title: The Local Government Reorganisation (Property) (West Midlands) Order 1988
entry.summary: This Order transfers property, rights and liabilities formerly vested in the West Midlands County Council to the councils of districts in that county and to the West Midlands Police Authority. The transfers effected are in addition to those effected on 22nd July 1987 by S.I. 1987/1077.

entry.title: The Submarine Pipe-lines (Designated Owners) (No. 3) Order 1988
entry.summary: This Order designates the companies listed in Part I of the Schedule as owners of the pipe-lines described in Part II of the Schedule, which lie above the Montrose oilfield, east of the coast of Scotland.
